This folder contains

00_README
        this file

MCS2012_mstKruskal.py
        python module that implements Kruskal's
        algorithm for computing an MST of a 
        given weighted undirected graph

MCS2012_uGraphWeighted.py
        python module implementing weighted undirected graph

MCS2012_scaleFreeGraph.py
        python module implementing scale free graphs

MCS2012_mst_example1.py
        python sctipt to compute the MST for
        an undirected weighted graph, specified
        in an input file similar to the file
        exampleGraph.txt below

MCS2012_mst_example2.py
        python script to perform the simulations
        for Figs. 5a-d

MCS2012_mst_example3.py
        python script to produce the example
        MSTs of Figs. 4a,b

MCS2012_mst_example4.py
        python script to perform the simulations
        for Fig. 5e

exampleGraph.edgList
        example graph, represented as edge list 

PP
        folder containing the simulation results and 
        gnuplot scripts needed to produce Figs 5 a-e 
